Dear <%= @customer.name %>,

Your order, Order #<%= @order.id %>, is ready for pickup and payment.  It includes the following items and combos:

<%= "Items:" if @order.item.present? %>
<% @order.item.each do |order_item| %>
<%= order_item.name %>
<% end if @order.item.present? %>

<%= "Combinations:" if @order.combo.present? %>
<% @order.combo.each do |combo| %>
<%= "Combo name: " + combo.name %>
<%  combo.combo_items.each do | combo_item | %>
<%=    combo_item.item.name %>
<%  end %>
<% end if @order.combo.present? %>
as a total price, including all discounts and taxes, of <%= number_to_currency(@order.total / 100.to_d) %>.

Thanks for giving us the chance to serve you!
